don't think Google want to leave operations in China, however maybe this is the leverage that could make the government change their mind?... \u003cspan style\u003d\"font-style: italic;\"\u003e...I think not.\u003c/span\u003e\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eI really wonder whether the Chinese Government would allow Google to remove it's censorship? If they do I get the feeling they might take the step of ultimately censoring internet access further up the chain, from behind the scenes.\u003cbr /\u003e\u003cbr /\u003eIt will be interesting to see how this pans out. What do you think will come of this latest news from Google?\u003cdiv class\u003d\"blogger-post-footer\"\u003e\u003cimg width\u003d'1' height\u003d'1' src\u003d'https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/567282840128827076-9014000279497525035?l\u003ddiscoveringmandarin.blogspot.com' alt\u003d'' /\u003e\u003c/div\u003e"},"link":[{"rel":"replies","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http://discoveringmandarin.blogspot.com/feeds/9014000279497525035/comments/default","title":"Post Comments"},{"rel":"replies","type":"text/html","href":"http://www.blogger.com/comment.g?blogID\u003d567282840128827076\u0026postID\u003d9014000279497525035\u0026isPopup\u003dtrue","title":"0 Comments"},{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/567282840128827076/posts/default/9014000279497525035"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/567282840128827076/posts/default/9014000279497525035"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"http://discoveringmandarin.blogspot.com/2010/01/google-to-stop-censoring-or-to-leave.html","title":"Google To Stop Censoring? Or to Leave China?"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"Charlie @ Discovering Mandarin"},"uri":{"$t":"http://www.blogger.com/profile/03151219439636084759"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"32","height":"30","src":"http://3.bp.blogs